1
00:00:00,950 --> 00:00:04,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The more time you spend with someone, 
the more you invariably learn about them.</i></font>

2
00:00:06,870 --> 00:00:09,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Her soul is in the early teens at most.</i></font>

3
00:00:10,240 --> 00:00:14,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Most of her knowledge's from the internet,
with very little first-hand experience.</i></font>

4
00:00:15,380 --> 00:00:17,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>She's usually stupidly 
bright and cheerful,</i></font>

5
00:00:19,490 --> 00:00:20,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>but at times,</i></font>

6
00:00:20,890 --> 00:00:23,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>she has a look of total resignation 
on her face.</i></font>

7
00:00:24,730 --> 00:00:27,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Perhaps her previous life wasn't one 
she could look back fondly upon.</i></font>

8
00:00:28,590 --> 00:00:29,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Still...</i></font>

9
00:00:29,430 --> 00:00:32,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aqua, Ruby, dinner's ready.</font>

10
00:00:32,710 --> 00:00:33,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Coming!</font>

11
00:00:36,010 --> 00:00:38,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Now that we've been reincarnated,</i></font>

12
00:00:38,840 --> 00:00:42,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>as long as we're both living our best 
lives now, none of that matters.</i></font>

13
00:00:44,020 --> 00:00:47,360
<font size="36" color="#070508"><b>{\an5}m 0 0 l 0 102 32 102 b 3 75 3 32 32 0</b></font>

14
00:00:44,020 --> 00:00:47,360
<font size="36" color="#070508"><b>{\an5}<font face="Georgia">OSHI <font color="#cb0085">NO <font color="#070508">KO</font></font></font></b></font>

15
00:00:44,020 --> 00:00:47,360
<font size="36" color="#070508"><b>{\an5}m 0 0 l 0 102 32 102 b 3 75 3 32 32 0</b></font>

16
00:02:14,430 --> 00:02:16,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The curry here is great!</font>

17
00:02:17,240 --> 00:02:21,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Check this out! The marrow-less bones 
can be used as straws!</font>

18
00:02:22,500 --> 00:02:24,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can even drink your lassi with them!</font>

19
00:02:28,030 --> 00:02:28,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow!</font>

20
00:02:28,910 --> 00:02:30,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's true! This is great!</font>

21
00:02:30,420 --> 00:02:31,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right?</font>

22
00:02:31,690 --> 00:02:33,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where should we go next?</font>

23
00:02:33,420 --> 00:02:35,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Everyone here is expecting to drink.</font>

24
00:02:35,820 --> 00:02:40,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hmm, places nearby 
where we could drink in peace?</font>

25
00:02:40,150 --> 00:02:40,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How about Pater?</font>

26
00:02:41,210 --> 00:02:43,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, I like it.</font>

27
00:02:43,580 --> 00:02:47,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A friend of mine runs that bar. 
I'll shoot them a LINE message.</font>

28
00:02:48,930 --> 00:02:49,820
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="16"><font color="#fefbfe">Aqua Hoshino</font></font></b></font>

29
00:02:50,220 --> 00:02:51,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Excuse me a second.</font>

30
00:02:51,950 --> 00:02:53,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey. What's up?</font>

31
00:02:53,560 --> 00:02:54,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where are you?</font>

32
00:02:54,990 --> 00:02:58,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You haven't checked 
any of the items due today.</font>

33
00:02:58,210 --> 00:03:01,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Uh, I'm out drinking 
with the marketing rep.</i></font>

34
00:03:02,020 --> 00:03:03,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Marketing rep?</font>

35
00:03:03,740 --> 00:03:08,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>So they brought a bunch of "friends" 
who are models and actresses,</i></font>

36
00:03:08,860 --> 00:03:11,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>and you're drinking at a hideaway bar?</i></font>

37
00:03:14,550 --> 00:03:18,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I mean, networking is part of their job.</font>

38
00:03:19,190 --> 00:03:22,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And we always need good actors.</font>

39
00:03:22,160 --> 00:03:23,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm not against it,</i></font>

40
00:03:24,030 --> 00:03:27,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>but these things tend to be 
full of tough customers.</i></font>

41
00:03:28,240 --> 00:03:29,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't get eaten alive.</font>

42
00:03:33,200 --> 00:03:37,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course. How many years do you 
think I've spent in this business?</font>

43
00:03:43,770 --> 00:03:48,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's a lot about work that 
comes down to human feeling.</font>

44
00:03:48,770 --> 00:03:51,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Some things you can only see 
with alcohol in your system, too.</font>

45
00:03:52,710 --> 00:03:57,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This world runs on communication, 
and I'm a pro here.</font>

46
00:03:59,840 --> 00:04:03,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And pros never lose themselves in booze.</font>

47
00:04:03,140 --> 00:04:06,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? My phone's gone!</font>

48
00:04:06,390 --> 00:04:07,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where'd it go?</font>

49
00:04:08,290 --> 00:04:11,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your phone's right here, Director Gotanda.</font>

50
00:04:13,200 --> 00:04:13,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aqua-kun.</font>

51
00:04:14,360 --> 00:04:15,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Could you drag that thing home?</font>

52
00:04:15,710 --> 00:04:17,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sure. I'll make sure the skunk gets home.</font>

53
00:04:17,910 --> 00:04:19,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, hey, kid.</font>

54
00:04:19,390 --> 00:04:21,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you Aqua Hoshino-kun?</font>

55
00:04:21,430 --> 00:04:25,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've heard all about you. 
You're the director's best student?</font>

56
00:04:24,810 --> 00:04:26,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Woohoo!</font>

57
00:04:25,230 --> 00:04:27,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No. I don't know this man.</font>

58
00:04:27,980 --> 00:04:31,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now, now. It's raining 
outside, so join us.</font>

59
00:04:31,180 --> 00:04:32,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll call a taxi for you right away.</font>

60
00:04:33,030 --> 00:04:34,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you hungry?</font>

61
00:04:34,590 --> 00:04:39,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The Napolitan here is amazing. 
Eat that before you go, at least.</font>

62
00:04:39,460 --> 00:04:40,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, thank you.</font>

63
00:04:40,840 --> 00:04:43,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're always pestering the young ones.</font>

64
00:04:43,020 --> 00:04:44,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Give it a rest, Tendouji-san.</font>

65
00:04:46,180 --> 00:04:48,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't go giving me a bad name, now.</font>

66
00:04:51,120 --> 00:04:53,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tendouji... Marina Tendouji?</font>

67
00:04:53,860 --> 00:04:55,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why, yes.</font>

68
00:05:03,470 --> 00:05:06,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did I give you my name?</font>

69
00:05:07,580 --> 00:05:09,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here you are. Club soda.</font>

70
00:05:09,620 --> 00:05:13,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's go drinking as soon 
as you're old enough.</font>

71
00:05:13,330 --> 00:05:17,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I guess you wouldn't want 
to go with an old lady like me.</font>

72
00:05:17,230 --> 00:05:21,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't worry. I'll bring 
some cute friends with me.</font>

73
00:05:24,400 --> 00:05:26,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You must love drinking.</font>

74
00:05:26,340 --> 00:05:30,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's part of my job, in a way.</font>

75
00:05:30,000 --> 00:05:31,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is that really okay?</font>

76
00:05:33,320 --> 00:05:36,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Doesn't your family worry?</font>

77
00:05:36,140 --> 00:05:39,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, I'm in my mid-fifties.</font>

78
00:05:39,170 --> 00:05:44,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And I've been doing this forever, 
so none of them worry about me.</font>

79
00:05:46,660 --> 00:05:47,530
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font face="Comic Sans MS"><font color="#623f53"></font></font></b>May I get to go to a B-Komachi concert</font>

80
00:05:47,530 --> 00:05:48,540
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font face="Comic Sans MS"><font color="#3a445d"></font></font></b>May I get permission to go outside</font>

81
00:05:48,540 --> 00:05:53,540
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font face="Comic Sans MS"><font color="#474247"></font></font></b>May Mom and Dad stay healthy
and never get sick</font>

82
00:05:54,170 --> 00:05:56,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You know somebody out there does.</font>

83
00:05:56,600 --> 00:05:58,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I suppose.</font>

84
00:05:58,300 --> 00:06:00,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm married.</font>

85
00:06:00,700 --> 00:06:03,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">See, this is my family!</font>

86
00:06:06,470 --> 00:06:09,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>How is this even possible?</i></font>

87
00:06:11,100 --> 00:06:14,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Are there really parents like her?</i></font>

88
00:06:20,160 --> 00:06:23,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Sarina-chan...</i></font>

89
00:06:23,450 --> 00:06:28,910
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font face="Comic Sans MS"><font color="#f5adaa">Happy 54th, <font color="#eb65a6">Mom!
<font color="#f9fba4">Don't drink too much</font></font></font></font></b></font>

90
00:06:24,350 --> 00:06:26,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Your life must've been a living hell.</i></font>

91
00:06:27,390 --> 00:06:28,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When you have kids,</font>

92
00:06:29,210 --> 00:06:32,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">all that matters 
is that they stay healthy.</font>

93
00:06:33,500 --> 00:06:36,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mom... That's why Mom won't come...</font>

94
00:06:36,580 --> 00:06:37,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No.</font>

95
00:06:37,650 --> 00:06:39,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're stuck on this bit again.</font>

96
00:06:40,420 --> 00:06:42,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Listen, in this scene,</font>

97
00:06:42,230 --> 00:06:46,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">you're a child who starts to understand 
her mother who ran away from her.</font>

98
00:06:46,350 --> 00:06:50,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You admit that you're abnormal, 
and that your mother doesn't love you.</font>

99
00:06:51,750 --> 00:06:56,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You let her go, and you set yourself 
free in the process, too.</font>

100
00:06:57,170 --> 00:07:01,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You need to look relieved, not desperate.</font>

101
00:07:00,360 --> 00:07:01,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}But that's all wrong.</font>

102
00:07:03,560 --> 00:07:08,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Admitting your mother doesn't love you? 
That can't be right.</font>

103
00:07:09,110 --> 00:07:11,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's probably just a misunderstanding.</font>

104
00:07:12,370 --> 00:07:16,370
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="14"><font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#241916">The 15-Year Lie</font></font></font></b></font>

105
00:07:12,820 --> 00:07:15,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This makes no sense to me.</font>

106
00:07:17,310 --> 00:07:19,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I mean, after all...</font>

107
00:07:19,980 --> 00:07:22,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Deep down,</font>

108
00:07:22,910 --> 00:07:25,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">parents always love their kids.</font>

109
00:07:28,530 --> 00:07:29,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Ibaraki.</i></font>

110
00:07:29,870 --> 00:07:33,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Perform at a joint concert 
on an outdoor stage starting 6 PM.</i></font>

111
00:07:34,170 --> 00:07:35,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Get in the car at 9 PM.</i></font>

112
00:07:36,350 --> 00:07:38,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Back home at 11 PM.</i></font>

113
00:07:38,440 --> 00:07:40,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Go to school at 8:30 AM.</i></font>

114
00:07:40,590 --> 00:07:42,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Leave early at 10:30 AM.</i></font>

115
00:07:42,570 --> 00:07:48,530
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="15"><font face="Arial Black"><font color="#4b3b23">Dig Deep!
Chase the Impawsible!!</font></font></font></b></font>

116
00:07:42,570 --> 00:07:48,530
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="15"><font face="Arial Black"><font color="#d42727">Dig Deep!
<font color="#4c8b9f">Chase the Impawsible!!</font></font></font></font></b></font>

117
00:07:42,570 --> 00:07:47,520
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="21"><font face="Arial Black"><font color="#c3d0cd">Esperanto Lesson</font></font></font></b></font>

118
00:07:42,570 --> 00:07:45,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i></i>Dig Deep! Chase the Impawsible!<i> 
prep meeting at 11:30 AM.</i></font>

119
00:07:46,220 --> 00:07:48,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Film a report at 12 PM.</i></font>

120
00:07:49,110 --> 00:07:51,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Get in the car at 3 PM, have lunch,</i></font>

121
00:07:51,650 --> 00:07:55,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>approve interview text, 
and study for finals.</i></font>

122
00:07:55,620 --> 00:07:57,330
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font face="Comic Sans MS"><font color="#372d33">Yamada        Tanaka        Hoshino        Sasaki        Inoue</font></font></b></font>

123
00:07:56,350 --> 00:07:57,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And at 4 PM,</i></font>

124
00:07:57,670 --> 00:08:01,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>attend taping for a late-night 
variety show. Film three episodes.</i></font>

125
00:08:02,890 --> 00:08:05,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Practice choreo for a new song at 9:30 PM.</i></font>

126
00:08:06,430 --> 00:08:09,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And at the same time, 
discuss YouTube video ideas.</i></font>

127
00:08:09,780 --> 00:08:12,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>One-on-one acting lessons at 11 PM.</i></font>

128
00:08:13,590 --> 00:08:16,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Go to bed at 3 AM.</i></font>

129
00:08:28,430 --> 00:08:32,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mom did all this without breaking a sweat.</font>

130
00:08:33,220 --> 00:08:34,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I need to do better.</font>

131
00:08:35,330 --> 00:08:39,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's okay. I know I can do this.</font>

132
00:08:42,380 --> 00:08:44,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's very little time 
before we start filming.</font>

133
00:08:45,010 --> 00:08:49,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd like you to pack Ruby-san's 
schedule with acting lessons.</font>

134
00:08:49,610 --> 00:08:52,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ruby's doing all she can.</font>

135
00:08:52,090 --> 00:08:56,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Her schedule's already packed. 
She barely gets enough sleep.</font>

136
00:08:56,200 --> 00:08:57,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even yesterday...</font>

137
00:08:57,520 --> 00:09:00,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Reduce the amount of work she takes on.</font>

138
00:09:00,300 --> 00:09:02,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Especially for the duration 
of filming and rehearsals.</font>

139
00:09:03,650 --> 00:09:07,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The 15-Year Lie</i> will be 
a real test of acting chops.</font>

140
00:09:07,710 --> 00:09:12,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It might be cruel to say this about 
an actor as inexperienced as Ruby-san,</font>

141
00:09:12,610 --> 00:09:16,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but even I can see that 
she's lacking in ability.</font>

142
00:09:18,700 --> 00:09:22,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Where does he get off saying that when he 
produced that </i>Sweet Today<i> live-action?</i></font>

143
00:09:24,190 --> 00:09:26,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But he's not wrong.</i></font>

144
00:09:27,260 --> 00:09:31,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Ruby doesn't have the skill 
to lead a cast that good.</i></font>

145
00:09:34,340 --> 00:09:36,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hoist the sails, mateys!</font>

146
00:09:36,380 --> 00:09:38,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Onward ho! To a brand new world!</font>

147
00:09:41,800 --> 00:09:43,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not so fast!</font>

148
00:09:43,600 --> 00:09:47,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Only one of us can get her hands on 
that singular, legendary treasure!</font>

149
00:09:47,690 --> 00:09:50,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And I'll make sure it won't be you!</font>

150
00:09:50,370 --> 00:09:52,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hah! Try me!</font>

151
00:09:56,280 --> 00:09:57,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's so hot!</i></font>

152
00:09:57,240 --> 00:09:58,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's so hot!</i></font>

153
00:10:01,460 --> 00:10:04,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When summer blazes hot, 
make sweat walk the plank...</font>

154
00:10:04,660 --> 00:10:09,420
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="12"><font color="#7e8283">Body Wipes</font></font></b></font>

155
00:10:04,660 --> 00:10:09,420
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="12"><font color="#c180bf">Soap Scented</font></font></b></font>

156
00:10:04,660 --> 00:10:09,420
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font face="Times New Roman"><font size="16"><font color="#648ee7">Spectaclean Body Wipes</font></font></font></b></font>

157
00:10:04,660 --> 00:10:09,420
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="11"><font color="#f7f7f7">Smooth skin
in a jiffy!</font></font></b></font>

158
00:10:04,710 --> 00:10:06,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">...with Spectaclean Body Wipes!</font>

159
00:10:06,710 --> 00:10:09,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cut! That's perfect!</font>

160
00:10:09,690 --> 00:10:11,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Keep going!</font>

161
00:10:11,970 --> 00:10:18,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I offered you the ad 'cause a big sponsor 
has a <i>Tokyo Blade</i> fan for a daughter,</font>

162
00:10:18,140 --> 00:10:19,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and you two did great!</font>

163
00:10:19,600 --> 00:10:21,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}I'm honored!</font>

164
00:10:19,600 --> 00:10:21,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm honored!</font>

165
00:10:21,380 --> 00:10:24,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow, you're in perfect sync. 
Your bad blood's all kayfabe, then?</font>

166
00:10:26,570 --> 00:10:30,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Haha! Of course it is!</font>

167
00:10:26,570 --> 00:10:30,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Haha! Of course it is!</font>

168
00:10:30,030 --> 00:10:32,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A rival? Who, her?</font>

169
00:10:32,700 --> 00:10:34,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not a chance. 
She's nowhere near good enough.</font>

170
00:10:34,780 --> 00:10:38,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wha? You got into it too, Kana-chan.</font>

171
00:10:38,610 --> 00:10:40,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't call me that!</font>

172
00:10:43,430 --> 00:10:47,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So, what'd you think? Did it help?</font>

173
00:10:48,040 --> 00:10:50,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You two really are amazing.</font>

174
00:10:50,650 --> 00:10:53,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You showed me how far I still have to go.</font>

175
00:10:53,930 --> 00:10:56,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How can I act like you?</font>

176
00:10:58,110 --> 00:11:00,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Know yourself.</font>

177
00:11:01,000 --> 00:11:05,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You need to have a good grasp 
of who you are on the inside.</font>

178
00:11:06,170 --> 00:11:07,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who I am on the inside?</font>

179
00:11:08,360 --> 00:11:13,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">For example, you take 
your likes and dislikes,</font>

180
00:11:13,770 --> 00:11:17,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and you either exaggerate 
or play them down as needed.</font>

181
00:11:17,790 --> 00:11:18,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right.</font>

182
00:11:18,930 --> 00:11:24,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That way, you can form new rules 
and associations within your emotions.</font>

183
00:11:25,180 --> 00:11:26,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's how you establish a character—</font>

184
00:11:27,160 --> 00:11:29,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">the thing you're having 
trouble with right now.</font>

185
00:11:29,400 --> 00:11:34,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I place more emphasis on the 
character than myself, though.</font>

186
00:11:34,090 --> 00:11:37,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That much is obvious. 
You're a method actor.</font>

187
00:11:40,410 --> 00:11:43,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Know myself?</i></font>

188
00:11:44,190 --> 00:11:46,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What kind of person </i>am<i> I?</i></font>

189
00:11:48,510 --> 00:11:50,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Am I Ruby?</i></font>

190
00:11:52,350 --> 00:11:55,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Am I Sarina Tendouji?</i></font>

191
00:11:57,110 --> 00:11:58,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Who am I?</i></font>

192
00:11:58,570 --> 00:12:00,820
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="15"><font color="#0e1117">Ichigo: Do you never think about meeting your mom?
Ai: Well, my mother hates me.
Ai: So I probably shouldn't. That's what's better for her, too.</font></font></b></font>

193
00:12:02,320 --> 00:12:05,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mother doesn't love me.</font>

194
00:12:06,690 --> 00:12:09,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No. That can't be true.</font>

195
00:12:10,190 --> 00:12:11,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I mean...</font>

196
00:12:17,970 --> 00:12:18,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mother!</font>

197
00:12:19,630 --> 00:12:23,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You came to see me! 
How long will you be staying?</font>

198
00:12:24,170 --> 00:12:29,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">After I stop by your grandma's place, 
I have to head back to Tokyo.</font>

199
00:12:31,170 --> 00:12:35,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh. You must be busy with work.</font>

200
00:12:35,500 --> 00:12:36,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry.</font>

201
00:12:36,950 --> 00:12:39,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I need to go speak to your doctor.</font>

202
00:12:39,610 --> 00:12:42,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, okay...</font>

203
00:12:47,680 --> 00:12:49,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, Mother?</font>

204
00:12:53,810 --> 00:12:57,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you love me?</font>

205
00:12:58,950 --> 00:13:00,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I mean...</i></font>

206
00:13:01,840 --> 00:13:05,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>There's no way those words were a lie.</i></font>

207
00:13:05,700 --> 00:13:08,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course I love you.</font>

208
00:13:15,980 --> 00:13:17,980
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="32"><font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#aba0a6">Tendouji</font></font></font></b></font>

209
00:13:18,340 --> 00:13:21,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Many times, I found myself standing 
here when I was feeling down.</i></font>

210
00:13:22,690 --> 00:13:26,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>My home still stood at the address 
I remembered it at.</i></font>

211
00:13:28,440 --> 00:13:32,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>If I rang the bell, Mother would answer.</i></font>

212
00:13:33,630 --> 00:13:36,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>So many times, I thought about 
pressing that button and saying...</i></font>

213
00:13:36,880 --> 00:13:41,340
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="12"><font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#838383">Tendouji</font></font></font></b></font>

214
00:13:38,390 --> 00:13:40,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mother, it's me.</font>

215
00:13:42,610 --> 00:13:43,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But no.</i></font>

216
00:13:56,720 --> 00:14:02,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Once upon a time, there was 
a perfectly ordinary family.</font>

217
00:14:03,200 --> 00:14:06,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As much affection as the mother 
showered the daughter with,</font>

218
00:14:06,620 --> 00:14:10,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">she was found to have a serious 
illness when she was four.</font>

219
00:14:11,730 --> 00:14:17,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">After learning her daughter had less than 
a 10% chance of living another 10 years,</font>

220
00:14:17,270 --> 00:14:19,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">the mother treated her 
with love and care for a while,</font>

221
00:14:19,910 --> 00:14:23,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but in time, it broke her down mentally.</font>

222
00:14:24,970 --> 00:14:31,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The father separated the two and focused 
on helping the mother recover.</font>

223
00:14:32,440 --> 00:14:36,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They came from a respected family 
in the countryside,</font>

224
00:14:36,230 --> 00:14:39,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so they put the daughter in the care of 
the biggest hospital in their hometown.</font>

225
00:14:40,990 --> 00:14:45,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The parents threw themselves into work 
as if to run from their sorrows,</font>

226
00:14:45,270 --> 00:14:48,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and soon they would refuse 
to see reality for what it was.</font>

227
00:14:49,500 --> 00:14:53,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Eventually, they started to avert 
their eyes from their daughter, too.</font>

228
00:14:54,780 --> 00:14:57,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My mother used to be a figure skater!</font>

229
00:14:57,350 --> 00:15:01,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She says she'll teach me how 
to skate once I'm discharged!</font>

230
00:15:01,940 --> 00:15:06,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want to make the Olympics 
and put a smile on her face!</font>

231
00:15:07,790 --> 00:15:11,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The daughter's condition 
only grew worse with time.</font>

232
00:15:12,300 --> 00:15:14,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She battled chronic headaches and nausea,</font>

233
00:15:15,570 --> 00:15:19,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and she lost her sense of balance, 
which left her unable to walk.</font>

234
00:15:21,630 --> 00:15:25,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It affected her memory 
and situational awareness, too.</font>

235
00:15:26,340 --> 00:15:30,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">During those days of suffering, 
she found solace in one special girl.</font>

236
00:15:32,260 --> 00:15:36,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The daughter came to live 
vicariously through her.</font>

237
00:15:37,550 --> 00:15:43,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As her condition became terminal, 
the mother stopped showing up at all.</font>

238
00:15:44,520 --> 00:15:47,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She must not have wanted 
to see her daughter in pain.</font>

239
00:15:49,050 --> 00:15:54,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But the girl continued 
to wait for her mother.</font>

240
00:15:56,230 --> 00:16:01,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She continued to wait for her mother, 
believing that she still loved her.</font>

241
00:16:06,260 --> 00:16:08,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, it's just you, Sensei.</font>

242
00:16:08,820 --> 00:16:11,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Too bad it's just me.</font>

243
00:16:13,060 --> 00:16:15,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hmm? That's, uh, B-Komachi?</font>

244
00:16:15,830 --> 00:16:17,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They released a new single?</font>

245
00:16:17,430 --> 00:16:18,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yep!</font>

246
00:16:18,880 --> 00:16:24,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The young man had a habit of going to see 
patients who didn't get visitors</font>

247
00:16:24,220 --> 00:16:26,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and making small talk with them.</font>

248
00:16:27,190 --> 00:16:31,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's impossible to quantify just 
how much that helped the daughter.</font>

249
00:16:32,750 --> 00:16:36,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She had found two rays of hope.</font>

250
00:16:37,200 --> 00:16:43,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Though she would come 
to lose them both in time.</font>

251
00:16:38,100 --> 00:16:43,570
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="12"><font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#7d8e92">Ai's Fan for All Eternity!!!</font></font></font></b></font>

252
00:16:45,750 --> 00:16:50,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even as she spent most of her 
short life in a small room,</font>

253
00:16:51,320 --> 00:16:52,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">fought through the pain,</font>

254
00:16:53,410 --> 00:16:55,370
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="13"><font face="Georgia"><font color="#493736">B-Komachi</font></font></font></b></font>

255
00:16:53,800 --> 00:16:55,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and had her dreams shattered,</font>

256
00:16:56,070 --> 00:17:00,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">she still continued to wait for 
her mother, day after day.</font>

257
00:17:01,570 --> 00:17:03,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She continued to believe 
that she was loved.</font>

258
00:17:04,830 --> 00:17:06,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But even on the day it all ended,</font>

259
00:17:07,370 --> 00:17:10,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">in her final hours,</font>

260
00:17:10,030 --> 00:17:13,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">the mother did not appear before her.</font>

261
00:17:15,920 --> 00:17:19,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As she heard the news in silence 
in their Tokyo home,</font>

262
00:17:21,200 --> 00:17:24,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">what must've gone through 
the mother's mind?</font>

263
00:17:26,190 --> 00:17:29,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As a mother who ran 
and ran from her daughter,</font>

264
00:17:29,410 --> 00:17:32,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">what exactly did she even mean to her?</font>

265
00:17:34,820 --> 00:17:37,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Soon after the girl died,</font>

266
00:17:37,990 --> 00:17:40,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">the mother gave birth 
to a son and daughter.</font>

267
00:17:43,210 --> 00:17:45,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And now, they all live happily ever after.</font>

268
00:17:47,880 --> 00:17:50,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All's well that ends well.</font>

269
00:17:56,650 --> 00:18:01,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've never seen Mother 
smile like that before.</font>

270
00:18:02,710 --> 00:18:06,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I knew it. I knew it somewhere deep down.</font>

271
00:18:07,720 --> 00:18:10,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wanted her to love me.</font>

272
00:18:10,950 --> 00:18:15,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But she didn't love me!</font>

273
00:18:16,080 --> 00:18:19,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's why I saw Mom as a replacement.</font>

274
00:18:19,520 --> 00:18:22,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I pushed my disgusting wishes onto her.</font>

275
00:18:22,890 --> 00:18:24,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What the hell am I?!</font>

276
00:18:24,960 --> 00:18:28,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Everyone in my life ends up suffering!</font>

277
00:18:28,910 --> 00:18:31,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All I bring is misfortune!</font>

278
00:18:31,860 --> 00:18:35,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">To Mother, Mom, and Sensei...</font>

279
00:18:36,580 --> 00:18:41,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tell me, gods. Why did you 
reincarnate a plague like me?</font>

280
00:18:43,370 --> 00:18:46,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sensei, have you ever been to, 
like, Shibuya or Harajuku?</font>

281
00:18:47,060 --> 00:18:49,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah. I did go to college in Tokyo.</font>

282
00:18:49,920 --> 00:18:51,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's so cool!</font>

283
00:18:52,110 --> 00:18:54,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Those places are full of life, right?</font>

284
00:18:55,030 --> 00:18:58,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Filled with lots of people, 
and even talent scouts.</font>

285
00:18:59,510 --> 00:19:02,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ai said she got scouted in Shibuya, too!</font>

286
00:19:02,740 --> 00:19:03,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah?</font>

287
00:19:04,200 --> 00:19:07,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll show you around the place 
when you're better.</font>

288
00:19:07,020 --> 00:19:07,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Really?!</font>

289
00:19:08,410 --> 00:19:10,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're really cute,</font>

290
00:19:10,040 --> 00:19:12,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so I'm sure you'll get 
approached by scouts.</font>

291
00:19:13,010 --> 00:19:17,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I'll send scouts from underground idol
groups and other shady places packing.</font>

292
00:19:17,520 --> 00:19:21,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I'd love to be an idol, 
underground or not.</font>

293
00:19:21,620 --> 00:19:24,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want to be like Ai 
and wear stylish outfits,</font>

294
00:19:24,020 --> 00:19:27,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">sing cute songs, 
have the crowds do calls for me,</font>

295
00:19:28,020 --> 00:19:29,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">take the stage in huge venues,</font>

296
00:19:29,730 --> 00:19:32,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and put smiles on lots of people's faces!</font>

297
00:19:33,180 --> 00:19:34,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's so dreamy!</font>

298
00:19:34,500 --> 00:19:36,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not a chance.</font>

299
00:19:36,560 --> 00:19:39,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Show business is a scary place.</font>

300
00:19:39,140 --> 00:19:43,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I won't allow it unless you have a good 
agency repping and looking out for you.</font>

301
00:19:43,180 --> 00:19:45,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Jeez, you're too overprotective!</font>

302
00:19:54,200 --> 00:19:56,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why did I even become an idol?!</font>

303
00:19:58,550 --> 00:19:59,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Take it easy.</font>

304
00:20:00,040 --> 00:20:01,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Take a deep, long breath.</font>

305
00:20:02,590 --> 00:20:05,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You need to lie down. Can you stand?</font>

306
00:20:06,470 --> 00:20:07,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The script...</font>

307
00:20:08,130 --> 00:20:09,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where's my script?</font>

308
00:20:10,470 --> 00:20:12,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I need to rehearse.</font>

309
00:20:12,160 --> 00:20:13,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're in no state for that.</font>

310
00:20:14,230 --> 00:20:15,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come on, grab on to me.</font>

311
00:20:15,640 --> 00:20:17,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't want your help, Aqua!</font>

312
00:20:19,470 --> 00:20:23,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's right. The reason I'm an idol</font>

313
00:20:24,370 --> 00:20:29,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">is so I can make it to the top and find 
the guy who killed Mom and Sensei.</font>

314
00:20:30,120 --> 00:20:32,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">To avenge Mom and Sensei!</font>

315
00:20:33,200 --> 00:20:35,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll find him if it's the last thing I do.</font>

316
00:20:35,720 --> 00:20:38,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And I'll make him regret 
ever coming into this world!</font>

317
00:20:40,980 --> 00:20:42,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stop that.</font>

318
00:20:42,620 --> 00:20:47,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Living for revenge will bring you 
nothing but pain and suffering.</font>

319
00:20:47,990 --> 00:20:50,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's no need for you to do that.</font>

320
00:20:51,960 --> 00:20:52,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please.</font>

321
00:20:53,850 --> 00:20:56,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Forget about revenge 
and live your own life.</font>

322
00:20:57,530 --> 00:20:59,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't tell me what to do.</font>

323
00:21:00,010 --> 00:21:02,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Quit trying to act like my big bro now.</font>

324
00:21:02,640 --> 00:21:06,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't see you as real family.</font>

325
00:21:07,370 --> 00:21:12,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're total strangers. We just happened 
to be reborn in the same place.</font>

326
00:21:14,590 --> 00:21:17,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fine. You're free to think that.</font>

327
00:21:18,820 --> 00:21:21,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not about to call us 
brother and sister now.</font>

328
00:21:22,410 --> 00:21:24,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know I have no right to.</font>

329
00:21:25,430 --> 00:21:27,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And I'm fully aware 
that I'm being a hypocrite.</font>

330
00:21:28,450 --> 00:21:29,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But...</font>

331
00:21:29,830 --> 00:21:32,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not asking as Aqua Hoshino.</font>

332
00:21:32,990 --> 00:21:34,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please listen to <i>me,</i></font>

333
00:21:35,220 --> 00:21:36,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sarina-chan.</font>

334
00:21:38,000 --> 00:21:41,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know this isn't why 
you wanted to be an idol.</font>

335
00:21:42,180 --> 00:21:43,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You got out of that hospital room.</font>

336
00:21:44,290 --> 00:21:46,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're finally free to live 
the life you want.</font>

337
00:21:47,950 --> 00:21:50,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Didn't you want to be like Ai 
and wear stylish outfits,</font>

338
00:21:50,600 --> 00:21:53,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">sing cute songs, 
have the crowds do calls for you,</font>

339
00:21:53,980 --> 00:21:57,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">take the stage in huge venues, 
and put smiles on lots of people's faces?!</font>

340
00:21:58,030 --> 00:22:01,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Didn't you become an idol 
to make those dreams come true?!</font>

341
00:22:02,490 --> 00:22:07,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>A singular thought, "What if?" 
has crossed my mind time and time again.</i></font>

342
00:22:08,720 --> 00:22:11,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Every time I felt I saw 
traces of Sarina-chan in you,</i></font>

343
00:22:11,600 --> 00:22:13,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I turned around and beat myself up.</i></font>

344
00:22:14,310 --> 00:22:18,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I hated myself for ever having 
such self-serving fantasies.</i></font>

345
00:22:19,560 --> 00:22:22,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>After being powerless 
to do anything to help Sarina-chan,</i></font>

346
00:22:22,500 --> 00:22:24,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>there was no way I'd ever 
get a second chance.</i></font>

347
00:22:25,580 --> 00:22:28,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But all these years,</i></font>

348
00:22:28,790 --> 00:22:31,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I've treated you just like 
I would have treated her.</i></font>

349
00:22:32,430 --> 00:22:35,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Forget about revenge.</font>

350
00:22:36,140 --> 00:22:37,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm begging you, Ruby.</font>

351
00:22:39,310 --> 00:22:40,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why?</font>

352
00:22:41,530 --> 00:22:43,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why are you crying?</font>

353
00:22:44,340 --> 00:22:48,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why did you just call me Sarina?</font>

354
00:22:49,700 --> 00:22:53,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How do you know 
about that time in the hospital?</font>

355
00:22:54,670 --> 00:22:55,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tell me...</font>

356
00:22:56,780 --> 00:22:59,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Could it be...?</font>

357
00:23:01,140 --> 00:23:03,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you Sensei?</font>

358
00:23:08,870 --> 00:23:11,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've been looking for this.</font>

359
00:23:13,240 --> 00:23:15,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You held onto it for me, huh,</font>

360
00:23:16,350 --> 00:23:17,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sarina-chan?</font>

361
00:24:08,600 --> 00:24:11,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sensei!</font>

362
00:24:11,760 --> 00:24:15,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've always been this close?</font>

363
00:24:15,450 --> 00:24:16,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why?</font>

364
00:24:16,730 --> 00:24:18,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why did you never tell me?</font>

365
00:24:19,630 --> 00:24:23,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Uh, I wasn't sure until just now.</font>

366
00:24:23,140 --> 00:24:24,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You dummy!</font>

367
00:24:24,730 --> 00:24:26,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I worked so hard!</font>

368
00:24:26,930 --> 00:24:32,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I thought you'd find me if 
I called myself a B-Komachi idol.</font>

369
00:24:32,710 --> 00:24:37,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I always looked for you 
among the crowd at every event.</font>

370
00:24:37,290 --> 00:24:40,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I thought you might be 
somewhere out there watching,</font>

371
00:24:40,290 --> 00:24:43,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so I gave my all each time!</font>

372
00:24:43,880 --> 00:24:47,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was worried you'd forgotten 
all about Mom and B-Komachi,</font>

373
00:24:48,420 --> 00:24:51,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and that maybe you'd never find me.</font>

374
00:24:52,390 --> 00:24:56,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I called the hospital and 
they said you were missing.</font>

375
00:24:56,780 --> 00:24:58,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And then what?</font>

376
00:24:58,830 --> 00:25:01,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I find you dead in a cave?</font>

377
00:25:01,560 --> 00:25:04,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry. I put you through a lot.</font>

378
00:25:04,920 --> 00:25:10,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I trusted you, Aqua, but then 
you went and sold Mom out.</font>

379
00:25:10,910 --> 00:25:15,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It made me feel like I couldn't 
trust anybody in the world.</font>

380
00:25:15,660 --> 00:25:17,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I didn't forget.</font>

381
00:25:18,150 --> 00:25:23,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I told the world about Ai's secret and 
spurred the director to make this movie</font>

382
00:25:24,080 --> 00:25:26,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">all to get revenge for Ai.</font>

383
00:25:28,590 --> 00:25:32,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I thought I had to avenge Mom and you,</font>

384
00:25:32,890 --> 00:25:35,890
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="10"><font face="Arial Black"><font color="#575e65">Dig Deep!
Chase the Impawsible!!</font></font></font></b></font>

385
00:25:32,890 --> 00:25:35,890
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="10"><font face="Arial Black"><font color="#472e39">Dig Deep!
<font color="#325677">Chase the Impawsible!!</font></font></font></font></b></font>

386
00:25:32,890 --> 00:25:35,890
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="9"><font color="#223e57">Special Episode Pitch</font></font></b></font>

387
00:25:33,680 --> 00:25:35,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so I did lots of awful things.</font>

388
00:25:36,510 --> 00:25:38,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I told lots of lies.</font>

389
00:25:39,310 --> 00:25:42,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Every time I did, 
a pain shot through my chest,</font>

390
00:25:42,610 --> 00:25:45,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and I felt a knot in my stomach.</font>

391
00:25:46,350 --> 00:25:52,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The more I lied, the more I felt I was 
drifting away from what I wanted to be.</font>

392
00:25:52,950 --> 00:25:56,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ruby, that stuff is not you.</font>

393
00:25:57,520 --> 00:25:58,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But...</font>

394
00:25:58,820 --> 00:26:02,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mom always said idols 
were made up of lies.</font>

395
00:26:02,110 --> 00:26:04,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You and Ai are different people.</font>

396
00:26:06,750 --> 00:26:09,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stop chasing after her shadow.</font>

397
00:26:09,650 --> 00:26:11,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Live your own life.</font>

398
00:26:12,930 --> 00:26:14,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You don't have to lie about anything.</font>

399
00:26:16,810 --> 00:26:19,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You know, the truth is...</font>

400
00:26:19,770 --> 00:26:21,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It hurt.</font>

401
00:26:21,660 --> 00:26:27,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I thought I had to tell believable lies 
and be all smiles all the time like Mom.</font>

402
00:26:28,030 --> 00:26:30,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I thought I had to be like her.</font>

403
00:26:31,590 --> 00:26:36,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Being an idol wasn't 
all rainbows and sunshine at all.</font>

404
00:26:36,180 --> 00:26:40,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So many times, I thought it'd be so much 
easier if I could just forget about her.</font>

405
00:26:42,100 --> 00:26:46,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When I looked at the fans, sometimes 
I'd think back to her killer's face.</font>

406
00:26:46,750 --> 00:26:53,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I had all these nasty, 
disgusting thoughts,</font>

407
00:26:54,150 --> 00:26:58,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but I hid them all because 
I wanted to be loved.</font>

408
00:26:59,610 --> 00:27:04,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I hadn't changed at all from the time 
I spent hating the world in the hospital.</font>

409
00:27:05,570 --> 00:27:07,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How can that be good enough?</font>

410
00:27:07,690 --> 00:27:10,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Am I really good enough like that?</font>

411
00:27:11,400 --> 00:27:14,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I told you I'd be your 
number one fan, remember?</font>

412
00:27:15,550 --> 00:27:17,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I said that because,</font>

413
00:27:17,690 --> 00:27:20,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">even as you suffered in pain 
in that hospital room,</font>

414
00:27:20,910 --> 00:27:25,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">you still looked straight ahead with 
stars in your eyes and continued to dream.</font>

415
00:27:26,130 --> 00:27:29,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Back then, you shone far brighter 
than Ai ever did!</font>

416
00:27:34,730 --> 00:27:36,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good for you.</font>

417
00:27:36,130 --> 00:27:38,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now Ruby will bounce back,</font>

418
00:27:38,580 --> 00:27:41,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and you'll get to make your movie 
just like you wanted.</font>

419
00:27:42,320 --> 00:27:46,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This might just inspire her 
to even greater heights.</font>

420
00:27:47,060 --> 00:27:51,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If so, that would make me very happy, too.</font>

421
00:27:53,310 --> 00:27:54,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But...</font>

422
00:27:54,690 --> 00:27:57,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you really sure about this?</font>

423
00:27:58,280 --> 00:28:02,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It might've been easier for you 
if she'd continued to hate you.</font>

424
00:28:08,780 --> 00:28:10,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'll trust you, Onii-chan.</i></font>

425
00:28:11,720 --> 00:28:16,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'll trust that the girl you said you'd be 
a fan of can shine brighter than Mom.</i></font>

426
00:28:18,950 --> 00:28:20,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Also...</i></font>

427
00:28:20,340 --> 00:28:23,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I haven't forgotten those words.</i></font>

428
00:28:24,310 --> 00:28:28,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>You said you'd marry me once 
I turned sixteen, remember?</i></font>

429
00:28:31,410 --> 00:28:36,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sensei? I'm sixteen now.</font>

430
00:28:39,650 --> 00:28:41,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm wiped!</font>

431
00:28:42,110 --> 00:28:44,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Onii-chan, gimme some of your juice.</font>

432
00:28:44,440 --> 00:28:46,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No. Get your own.</font>

433
00:28:47,810 --> 00:28:51,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Too late. You snooze, you lose juice.</font>

434
00:28:51,730 --> 00:28:54,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ah, I'm coming back to life!</font>

435
00:28:54,130 --> 00:28:55,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Get off of me.</font>

436
00:28:55,020 --> 00:28:56,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're damp with sweat.</font>

437
00:28:56,290 --> 00:28:59,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, let me have this.</font>

438
00:28:59,490 --> 00:29:01,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What the hell happened?!</font>

439
00:29:01,040 --> 00:29:04,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whoa, you startled me. 
Why'd you start yelling out of nowhere?</font>

440
00:29:04,640 --> 00:29:06,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're the ones startled here!</font>

441
00:29:06,920 --> 00:29:08,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ever heard of personal space?</font>

442
00:29:08,580 --> 00:29:10,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You two are stuck together like glue!</font>

443
00:29:10,500 --> 00:29:14,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, you know how Onii-chan 
and I had been fighting lately?</font>

444
00:29:14,540 --> 00:29:17,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, we made up the other day,</font>

445
00:29:18,400 --> 00:29:20,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and now we're making up for lost time.</font>

446
00:29:20,180 --> 00:29:21,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">More like <i>over</i>compensating!</font>

447
00:29:21,740 --> 00:29:26,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're part of the problem, Aqua! 
Tell your sister off!</font>

448
00:29:26,770 --> 00:29:29,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I <i>could</i> do that, or I could just 
let her do whatever she wants.</font>

449
00:29:29,470 --> 00:29:31,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right. I forgot he was 
obsessed with his sister.</font>

450
00:29:31,750 --> 00:29:33,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We've always been thick as thieves!</font>

451
00:29:35,190 --> 00:29:36,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Get off of him already!</font>

452
00:29:36,800 --> 00:29:38,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hold it!</font>

453
00:29:38,650 --> 00:29:41,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're two hot twins 
that look hot together!</font>

454
00:29:41,220 --> 00:29:43,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lemme take pics for Insta!</font>

455
00:29:44,930 --> 00:29:47,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ugh, you engagement junkie.</font>

456
00:29:50,380 --> 00:29:52,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't. That was so friggin' weird.</font>

457
00:29:52,880 --> 00:29:55,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I could smell the degeneracy in the air.</font>

458
00:29:56,810 --> 00:30:00,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, Ruby's got a lot on her plate.</font>

459
00:30:00,450 --> 00:30:04,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I bet she just wanted somebody to lean on.</font>

460
00:30:04,660 --> 00:30:07,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She's using him as a crutch, basically.</font>

461
00:30:07,920 --> 00:30:11,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If it's only as bad as needing an 
emotional support, that's fine.</font>

462
00:30:11,540 --> 00:30:16,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But the only way to really fix it is to do 
something about her packed schedule.</font>

463
00:30:16,750 --> 00:30:18,710
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font face="Times New Roman"><font size="12"><font color="#402347">The 15-Year Lie</font></font></font></b></font>

464
00:30:16,750 --> 00:30:20,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Heck, she's actually 
hit a wall with her acting.</font>

465
00:30:20,030 --> 00:30:22,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She desperately needs more rehearsal time.</font>

466
00:30:22,870 --> 00:30:25,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm glad she seems to be feeling better,</font>

467
00:30:25,180 --> 00:30:28,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but motivation and high spirits won't be 
enough to get her through this movie.</font>

468
00:30:30,300 --> 00:30:36,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If anything, she's at even more risk 
now with this mental doping.</font>

469
00:30:36,150 --> 00:30:39,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If she goes too hard and breaks down, 
it'll have all been for naught.</font>

470
00:30:39,050 --> 00:30:40,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right you are.</font>

471
00:30:41,030 --> 00:30:44,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But this is Ruby's best chance 
to make a move at superstardom.</font>

472
00:30:45,120 --> 00:30:51,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sure, she has to juggle TV appearances, 
events, concerts, and acting lessons...</font>

473
00:30:51,240 --> 00:30:52,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And her studies, too.</font>

474
00:30:52,690 --> 00:30:53,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Studies!</font>

475
00:30:53,710 --> 00:30:56,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right, those exist!</font>

476
00:30:56,140 --> 00:30:58,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mine were so long ago that 
I forgot all about the concept!</font>

477
00:30:58,920 --> 00:31:02,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm amazed you managed to keep up 
your high school girl gimmick like that.</font>

478
00:31:02,920 --> 00:31:05,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Either way, it'll be hard 
to strike the right balance.</font>

479
00:31:05,830 --> 00:31:09,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All we can do is hope 
the president takes care of it.</font>

480
00:31:10,310 --> 00:31:13,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even if Strawberry Pro 
has experienced this before with Ai,</font>

481
00:31:13,810 --> 00:31:16,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">it was the previous president 
at the helm at the time.</font>

482
00:31:17,140 --> 00:31:21,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is probably a real test of 
President Miyako's ability, as well.</font>

483
00:31:22,110 --> 00:31:25,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right. We're very grateful.</font>

484
00:31:25,100 --> 00:31:29,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll take a good look at Ruby's 
schedule and get back to you.</font>

485
00:31:35,680 --> 00:31:41,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Covering a charity event for 
28-Hour TV? That's a huge gig.</font>

486
00:31:49,220 --> 00:31:51,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I can make room in her schedule.</i></font>

487
00:31:52,250 --> 00:31:55,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But do I really want to give 
Ruby even more work?</i></font>

488
00:31:56,730 --> 00:31:59,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Reduce the amount of work she takes on.</font>

489
00:31:59,840 --> 00:32:03,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Especially for the duration 
of filming and rehearsals.</font>

490
00:32:06,860 --> 00:32:09,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>There's so much to think about.</i></font>

491
00:32:13,700 --> 00:32:18,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Keep this marketing rep named Tendouji 
as far away from Ruby as possible.</font>

492
00:32:19,020 --> 00:32:20,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did something happen?</font>

493
00:32:21,160 --> 00:32:24,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She's kind of like a relative 
we have history with.</font>

494
00:32:25,130 --> 00:32:27,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Interacting with her 
could make Ruby unstable.</font>

495
00:32:27,990 --> 00:32:29,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A relative?</font>

496
00:32:30,070 --> 00:32:34,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I guess that does happen. 
Tokyo's a small world.</font>

497
00:32:35,310 --> 00:32:39,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Got it. I'll keep an eye out.</font>

498
00:32:39,790 --> 00:32:40,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks.</font>

499
00:32:46,260 --> 00:32:49,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I have to secure time for rehearsals.</i></font>

500
00:32:49,450 --> 00:32:51,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But I need to think about her health, too.</i></font>

501
00:32:52,030 --> 00:32:54,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And Kana graduates at the end of the year.</i></font>

502
00:32:54,620 --> 00:32:57,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>How do we replace her in B-Komachi?</i></font>

503
00:32:59,190 --> 00:33:02,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>As a business owner, 
I should push her as hard as I can.</i></font>

504
00:33:03,270 --> 00:33:05,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But what about as her mother?</i></font>

505
00:33:05,540 --> 00:33:06,630
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="16"><font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#e3425e">Congratulations
<font color="#3f373a"><font size="13">Entrance Ceremony
<font size="12">Youtou High School</font></font></font></font></font></font></b></font>

506
00:33:08,510 --> 00:33:11,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Showbiz is in a constant state of churn.</i></font>

507
00:33:11,350 --> 00:33:14,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Most entertainers end up 
as a flash in the pan.</i></font>

508
00:33:14,470 --> 00:33:19,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Even if you gain a little fame, it can 
all fade away in just a year's time.</i></font>

509
00:33:19,520 --> 00:33:26,900
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="20"><font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#e3425e">Congratulations
<font color="#3f373a"><font size="16">Entrance Ceremony
<font size="15">Youtou High School</font></font></font></font></font></font></b></font>

510
00:33:20,730 --> 00:33:24,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>There's no doubt that her efforts now</i></font>

511
00:33:24,030 --> 00:33:26,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>will decide the next ten years 
of Ruby's life and career.</i></font>

512
00:33:27,590 --> 00:33:32,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I believe more than anybody else that 
she's capable of reaching the very top.</i></font>

513
00:33:32,780 --> 00:33:34,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Listen, Mom!</font>

514
00:33:34,510 --> 00:33:35,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah?</font>

515
00:33:35,490 --> 00:33:38,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}I'm slowly getting the hang of dancing!</font>

516
00:33:37,270 --> 00:33:38,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right!</font>

517
00:33:38,450 --> 00:33:42,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Soon, we hit the Tokyo Dome! 
The stage of our dreams!</font>

518
00:33:39,030 --> 00:33:40,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Wow!</font>

519
00:33:40,120 --> 00:33:41,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Right?</font>

520
00:33:41,390 --> 00:33:43,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}You're a natural!</font>

521
00:33:45,480 --> 00:33:49,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ichigo, what would you have done?</font>

522
00:33:50,420 --> 00:33:53,140
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font face="Comic Sans MS"><font color="#baaeb2">Samidare</font></font></b></font>

523
00:33:56,260 --> 00:33:58,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Barkeep, get me the usual.</font>

524
00:33:58,800 --> 00:34:02,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, yeah. The meat'n'veggies set 
with a small rice.</font>

525
00:34:02,400 --> 00:34:04,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And some mixed veggie juice,</font>

526
00:34:04,690 --> 00:34:06,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">extra kale.</font>

527
00:34:06,380 --> 00:34:08,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Could you order some 
damn booze for a change?</font>

528
00:34:08,950 --> 00:34:11,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're not a diner.</font>

529
00:34:12,030 --> 00:34:16,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is the only place I can get 
a proper meal this late at night.</font>

530
00:34:17,520 --> 00:34:22,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Jeez. Take better care of yourself, 
or you'll die from overwork.</font>

531
00:34:22,270 --> 00:34:26,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd much rather that than let 
one of our talent die from overwork.</font>

532
00:34:27,130 --> 00:34:31,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are your kids eating right? 
They're really busy now, yeah?</font>

533
00:34:32,090 --> 00:34:38,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mhm. Their manager 
should be taking care of that.</font>

534
00:34:38,710 --> 00:34:40,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You left it all to someone else?</font>

535
00:34:40,980 --> 00:34:44,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you don't look them in the eye 
and keep your arms wide open,</font>

536
00:34:44,490 --> 00:34:46,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">you'll miss the crucial signs.</font>

537
00:34:47,470 --> 00:34:52,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I get that, but they never 
wear their hearts on their sleeve.</font>

538
00:34:53,400 --> 00:34:58,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My son's always deadpan, 
my daughter's always all smiles,</font>

539
00:34:58,900 --> 00:35:01,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and they never complain.</font>

540
00:35:02,190 --> 00:35:05,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have no way to tell 
what they're thinking deep down.</font>

541
00:35:05,570 --> 00:35:08,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not their real mother, after all.</font>

542
00:35:12,300 --> 00:35:16,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wanna watch them up close 
all the time too, you know!</font>

543
00:35:16,160 --> 00:35:19,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not built for all this brainy work!</font>

544
00:35:20,100 --> 00:35:22,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How I'd love to go back 
to being just a manager if I could!</font>

545
00:35:23,940 --> 00:35:26,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But this company needs me to do this!</font>

546
00:35:27,340 --> 00:35:29,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We don't have anybody else to rely on!</font>

547
00:35:30,570 --> 00:35:31,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Barkeep.</font>

548
00:35:31,940 --> 00:35:33,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Long time no—</font>

549
00:35:35,540 --> 00:35:37,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ichigo...?</font>

550
00:35:42,000 --> 00:35:43,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Get back here!</font>

551
00:35:43,160 --> 00:35:45,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll be back later!</font>

552
00:35:45,790 --> 00:35:47,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, yeah.</font>

553
00:35:49,000 --> 00:35:51,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tokyo's a small world, all right.</font>

554
00:35:57,720 --> 00:35:59,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hold it, you dolt!</font>

555
00:36:07,720 --> 00:36:09,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I finally found you.</font>

556
00:36:10,040 --> 00:36:11,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">M-Miyako...</font>

557
00:36:12,150 --> 00:36:13,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Calm down a se—</font>

558
00:36:14,170 --> 00:36:20,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you have any goddamn idea 
how I've felt all these years?</font>

559
00:36:21,550 --> 00:36:27,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You abandoned the promise you made me 
to run off and do what, you asshole?!</font>

560
00:36:35,340 --> 00:36:37,300
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font color="#f6f050">[Express] Shinjuku Station</font></b></font>

561
00:36:42,880 --> 00:36:47,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The first time I saw Tokyo, it was covered 
in bright lights from top to bottom.</i></font>

562
00:36:48,130 --> 00:36:51,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It instantly stole my heart away.</i></font>

563
00:36:54,030 --> 00:36:58,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I felt that this city was where 
I was meant to live my life.</i></font>

564
00:36:59,470 --> 00:37:01,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The nightlife was like a video game.</i></font>

565
00:37:03,450 --> 00:37:07,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I took out the fodder, 
built up XP and gold,</i></font>

566
00:37:07,750 --> 00:37:09,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>leveled up,</i></font>

567
00:37:09,950 --> 00:37:12,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>bought more powerful weapons,</i></font>

568
00:37:13,750 --> 00:37:18,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>spent increasingly more time 
around stupidly loaded people,</i></font>

569
00:37:18,870 --> 00:37:21,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>started seeing the guys in college 
as snot-nosed brats,</i></font>

570
00:37:22,220 --> 00:37:29,350
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font color="#252840">m 0 0 l 100 0 100 100 0 100</font></b></font>

571
00:37:22,220 --> 00:37:23,640
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font face="Courier New">A wild Self-Proclaimed Tech CEO appeared!
A wild Self-Proclaimed Investor appeared!</font></b></font>

572
00:37:22,890 --> 00:37:27,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}defeated stronger foes, 
built up lots more XP,</i></font>

573
00:37:23,720 --> 00:37:25,100
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font face="Courier New">Miyako used Blow Kiss!</font></b></font>

574
00:37:25,140 --> 00:37:26,390
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font face="Courier New">The Self-Proclaimed Tech CEO was defeated!
The Self-Proclaimed Investor was defeated!</font></b></font>

575
00:37:26,470 --> 00:37:27,930
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font face="Courier New">Miyako leveled up!</font></b></font>

576
00:37:27,440 --> 00:37:29,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}leveled up even more,</i></font>

577
00:37:28,020 --> 00:37:29,350
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font face="Courier New">Miyako evolved from
cabaret club girl to lounge girl!</font></b></font>

578
00:37:29,350 --> 00:37:32,850
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font face="Arial Black"><font color="#f4b618">Cabaret Club</font></font></b></font>

579
00:37:29,660 --> 00:37:32,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>switched classes, and grew stronger.</i></font>

580
00:37:30,730 --> 00:37:32,850
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font face="Arial Black"><font color="#808efa">Lounge</font></font></b></font>

581
00:37:32,060 --> 00:37:32,850
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font face="Arial Black"><font color="#f17806">Hostess Club</font></font></b></font>

582
00:37:33,220 --> 00:37:36,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Tokyo's good to strong people like that,</i></font>

583
00:37:36,570 --> 00:37:39,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>and it affirmed my way of life.</i></font>

584
00:37:40,490 --> 00:37:45,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I played the game smart and 
followed this city's unspoken rules,</i></font>

585
00:37:46,400 --> 00:37:50,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>and I was sure I'd keep 
climbing to ever greater heights.</i></font>

586
00:37:54,670 --> 00:37:56,380
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="16"><font color="#8c4844">The hottest, "biggest" new face</font></font></b></font>

587
00:37:54,670 --> 00:37:56,380
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="16"><font color="#8c4844">Dynamite College Girl!!</font></font></b></font>

588
00:37:58,340 --> 00:38:01,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But it would all come crashing to an end.</i></font>

589
00:38:03,310 --> 00:38:05,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Tokyo was full of attractive girls,</i></font>

590
00:38:05,860 --> 00:38:10,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>and I didn't have that special 
something to make it in showbiz.</i></font>

591
00:38:11,740 --> 00:38:16,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I got more chances to interact with 
big shots due to being an entertainer,</i></font>

592
00:38:16,730 --> 00:38:18,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>but that didn't last long either.</i></font>

593
00:38:19,190 --> 00:38:21,650
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="12"><font face="Courier New"><font color="#a3a7a8">Checking Inbox</font></font></font></b></font>

594
00:38:19,190 --> 00:38:20,320
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="12"><font face="Courier New"><font color="#a3a7a8">Checking...</font></font></font></b></font>

595
00:38:19,480 --> 00:38:21,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>By the time I graduated college,</i></font>

596
00:38:20,320 --> 00:38:21,650
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="14"><font face="Courier New"><font color="#f6f8fa">No New Mail</font></font></font></b></font>

597
00:38:21,920 --> 00:38:25,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'd stopped getting invited 
to parties by business owners.</i></font>

598
00:38:26,990 --> 00:38:29,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Not that I cared.</i></font>

599
00:38:29,090 --> 00:38:31,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Those guys cheated at the drop of a hat.</i></font>

600
00:38:31,230 --> 00:38:33,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I would've never found happiness 
in life going out with them.</i></font>

601
00:38:34,630 --> 00:38:37,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>A Minato-ku trophy girl 
who was no longer in demand</i></font>

602
00:38:37,340 --> 00:38:42,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>could only stick around by becoming an 
intermediary who summoned younger girls.</i></font>

603
00:38:43,630 --> 00:38:46,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And I hung on pathetically 
by doing just that.</i></font>

604
00:38:47,920 --> 00:38:50,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>More and more men started 
asking me to be their mistress.</i></font>

605
00:38:52,130 --> 00:38:57,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Those scumbags are very good at sniffing 
out women at risk of losing their spot,</i></font>

606
00:38:57,540 --> 00:38:59,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>and they try to exploit them 
for all they're worth.</i></font>

607
00:39:01,060 --> 00:39:05,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>They use the starry-eyed girls 
until they get tired of them.</i></font>

608
00:39:05,700 --> 00:39:07,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hup.</font>

609
00:39:08,610 --> 00:39:09,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Heya.</font>

610
00:39:18,870 --> 00:39:23,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Listen, are you gonna keep 
working the night life forever?</font>

611
00:39:34,930 --> 00:39:38,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you don't have a goal in mind, 
wanna come work for me?</font>

612
00:39:49,700 --> 00:39:56,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I was a girl who longed for the bright 
lights but couldn't cut it in showbiz.</i></font>

613
00:39:54,080 --> 00:39:56,290
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="16"><font color="#563f32">Strawberry Productions</font></font></b></font>

614
00:39:56,660 --> 00:40:01,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>How ironic was it that I'd now be working 
to help others pursue their dreams?</i></font>

615
00:40:03,080 --> 00:40:03,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But...</i></font>

616
00:40:04,550 --> 00:40:08,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Seeing the lights from backstage 
didn't feel as bad as I'd thought.</i></font>

617
00:40:12,650 --> 00:40:13,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Miyako.</font>

618
00:40:15,400 --> 00:40:17,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Will you stay by my side and support me?</font>

619
00:40:18,990 --> 00:40:20,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll work my butt off.</font>

620
00:40:21,840 --> 00:40:24,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And if you'll be my pillar—my wife—</font>

621
00:40:24,550 --> 00:40:27,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll show you the most 
dazzling sight in the world.</font>

622
00:40:28,330 --> 00:40:30,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The most dazzling sight...?</font>

623
00:40:32,420 --> 00:40:34,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow!</font>

624
00:40:34,810 --> 00:40:38,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I bet it'd feel so good 
if we performed here.</font>

625
00:40:38,670 --> 00:40:42,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You mean <i>when</i> we perform here.</font>

626
00:40:42,170 --> 00:40:43,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right.</font>

627
00:40:43,160 --> 00:40:45,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's so huge.</font>

628
00:40:45,060 --> 00:40:46,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sure is.</font>

629
00:40:46,590 --> 00:40:48,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you actually think that?</font>

630
00:40:48,940 --> 00:40:50,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I do, I do.</font>

631
00:40:50,340 --> 00:40:52,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Really, now?</font>

632
00:40:52,230 --> 00:40:53,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Really! I mean it!</font>

633
00:40:53,800 --> 00:40:57,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">One day, we'll light up 
Tokyo Dome with glow sticks.</font>

634
00:40:58,450 --> 00:41:00,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's our dream.</font>

635
00:41:15,660 --> 00:41:18,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You said you'd show me!</font>

636
00:41:19,820 --> 00:41:24,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How could you just throw in the towel 
and run away from it all?!</font>

637
00:41:27,630 --> 00:41:32,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When I... I still haven't given up on it!</font>

638
00:41:36,310 --> 00:41:40,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You said it was our dream!</font>

639
00:41:51,010 --> 00:41:55,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So, Strawberry Productions will undergo 
a major organizational restructuring.</font>

640
00:41:56,240 --> 00:41:58,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Before that, 
I guess I should introduce you.</font>

641
00:42:01,870 --> 00:42:04,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's Ichigo Saitou-kun, 
our new errand boy.</font>

642
00:42:04,740 --> 00:42:06,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hello, I'm Saitou.</font>

643
00:42:07,710 --> 00:42:10,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">First, for your new assignments...</font>

644
00:42:10,860 --> 00:42:13,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Take a look at the handout.</font>

645
00:42:13,430 --> 00:42:15,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hayashi will handle 
the cross-media talent.</font>

646
00:42:16,010 --> 00:42:18,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Streamer Group A goes to Sasami,</font>

647
00:42:18,950 --> 00:42:20,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and Group B to Terabayashi.</font>

648
00:42:21,230 --> 00:42:24,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yoshizumi will manage 
MEM and Arima of B-Komachi.</font>

649
00:42:25,030 --> 00:42:29,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And I'll take over 
as Ruby and Aqua's manager.</font>

650
00:42:30,030 --> 00:42:31,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Everything else remains the same.</font>

651
00:42:31,870 --> 00:42:32,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

652
00:42:32,820 --> 00:42:36,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But then, who runs the agency?</font>

653
00:42:36,020 --> 00:42:37,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Beats me.</font>

654
00:42:38,290 --> 00:42:41,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Maybe that errand boy over there 
will take care of it.</font>

655
00:42:43,470 --> 00:42:45,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who is that?</font>

656
00:42:45,110 --> 00:42:48,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The president's husband. 
The one who founded this agency.</font>

657
00:42:48,270 --> 00:42:49,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?!</font>

658
00:42:50,510 --> 00:42:52,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's all from me. Back to work.</font>

659
00:42:59,040 --> 00:43:01,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good for you! You got to talk 
things out with Miyako-san!</font>

660
00:43:01,820 --> 00:43:05,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't believe you can say that 
after seeing this face.</font>

661
00:43:05,020 --> 00:43:07,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was half coerced into it.</font>

662
00:43:07,580 --> 00:43:09,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She threatened to sue me,</font>

663
00:43:09,340 --> 00:43:11,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and when I tried to argue, 
she literally threw hands.</font>

664
00:43:12,100 --> 00:43:14,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But you came back anyway.</font>

665
00:43:14,840 --> 00:43:17,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm happy for you. 
You wanted to all along, didn't you?</font>

666
00:43:22,480 --> 00:43:26,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You got me so much work, even 
though you weren't an agent here.</font>

667
00:43:26,930 --> 00:43:30,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Easier to do that when you're 
officially part of the agency, right?</font>

668
00:43:31,550 --> 00:43:34,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's not it. I was set up.</font>

669
00:43:36,000 --> 00:43:37,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">By whom?</font>

670
00:43:37,420 --> 00:43:39,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aqua, who else?</font>

671
00:43:39,600 --> 00:43:42,350
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font color="#99aacd">m 0 0 l 100 0 100 100 0 100</font></b></font>

672
00:43:39,600 --> 00:43:42,350
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font color="#2e2f4a"><font size="10">< Aqua Hoshino</font></font></b></font>

673
00:43:39,600 --> 00:43:42,350
<font size="18" color="#424242">{\an7}<font size="10">We need to talk about Ruby</font></font>

674
00:43:39,600 --> 00:43:42,350
<font size="18" color="#424242">{\an7}<font size="10">Can you come to Samidare
at 2 AM tonight?</font></font>

675
00:43:39,600 --> 00:43:42,350
<font size="18" color="#0a5107">{\an7}<font size="10">Talk about sudden</font></font>

676
00:43:39,600 --> 00:43:42,350
<font size="18" color="#0a5107">{\an7}<font size="10">Should a high schooler
really be in the night-life
district that late at night?</font></font>

677
00:43:39,600 --> 00:43:42,350
<font size="18" color="#424242">{\an7}<font size="10">Won't be a problem</font></font>

678
00:43:39,600 --> 00:43:42,350
<font size="18" color="#0a5107">{\an7}<font size="10">Fine
I might be a little late, though</font></font>

679
00:43:39,600 --> 00:43:42,310
<font size="18" color="#424242">{\an7}<font size="10">Thanks</font></font>

680
00:43:39,600 --> 00:43:42,310
<font size="18" color="#0a5107">{\an7}<font size="10">Don't let Miyako catch you</font></font>

681
00:43:39,600 --> 00:43:42,310
<font size="18" color="#0a5107">{\an7}<font size="10">I'm here</font></font>

682
00:43:42,390 --> 00:43:43,890
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="14"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><font color="#baaeb2">Samidare</font></font></font></b></font>

683
00:43:43,890 --> 00:43:48,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He was the one who summoned me 
to Miyako's favorite bar that night.</font>

684
00:43:50,740 --> 00:43:52,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And what do I find...</font>

685
00:43:57,320 --> 00:43:58,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aqua did that?</font>

686
00:44:00,260 --> 00:44:03,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, so that's what it was.</font>

687
00:44:05,960 --> 00:44:07,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I understand now.</i></font>

688
00:44:08,120 --> 00:44:10,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I knew it.</i></font>

689
00:44:11,310 --> 00:44:14,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Onii-chan loves me way too much!</i></font>

690
00:44:15,810 --> 00:44:19,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He dragged Ichigo-san back 
to the agency for my sake!</i></font>

691
00:44:19,140 --> 00:44:22,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>His methods are always 
so roundabout and so damn cute!</i></font>

692
00:44:22,430 --> 00:44:25,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He was like this even as a doctor.</i></font>

693
00:44:25,600 --> 00:44:29,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He'd set up surprises without 
talking to anyone about it.</i></font>

694
00:44:29,510 --> 00:44:32,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He's always been nice to a fault. 
No changing it now.</i></font>

695
00:44:32,950 --> 00:44:35,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And he still tries to pretend 
to be the bad guy.</i></font>

696
00:44:36,020 --> 00:44:38,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But don't worry! 
I get all that about you and more!</i></font>

697
00:44:43,670 --> 00:44:46,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, there's just too much 
on her schedule.</font>

698
00:44:46,110 --> 00:44:49,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But this is Ruby's chance 
to become a household name.</font>

699
00:44:49,990 --> 00:44:52,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What if work dries up for her later?</font>

700
00:44:52,780 --> 00:44:55,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then I'll just go out and get more.</font>

701
00:44:58,550 --> 00:45:00,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't lose sight of the big picture.</font>

702
00:45:00,920 --> 00:45:03,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't be afraid of her 
booming popularity ending.</font>

703
00:45:03,260 --> 00:45:05,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's a matter of when, not if.</font>

704
00:45:06,610 --> 00:45:10,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Relax. Ruby's no flash in the pan.</font>

705
00:45:10,660 --> 00:45:14,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And it's my job to make sure 
she stays that way.</font>

706
00:45:14,830 --> 00:45:19,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What we should be doing now 
is making Ruby seem exclusive.</font>

707
00:45:19,020 --> 00:45:22,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The showrunners need to see her 
as a premium talent.</font>

708
00:45:22,510 --> 00:45:26,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Give them the runaround and secure 
better-quality gigs for her.</font>

709
00:45:26,380 --> 00:45:31,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And if possible, focus on 
the gigs that are far in the future.</font>

710
00:45:31,100 --> 00:45:33,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't just accept any work 
that comes her way.</font>

711
00:45:33,700 --> 00:45:36,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just being on screen doesn't 
make one a household name.</font>

712
00:45:37,030 --> 00:45:40,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Only take on shows that are built 
to highlight Ruby's character.</font>

713
00:45:40,730 --> 00:45:42,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It was the same with Ai, too.</font>

714
00:45:42,870 --> 00:45:45,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can turn down all of these.</font>

715
00:45:45,430 --> 00:45:48,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Also, use her as a bargaining chip 
to barter deals for other talents.</font>

716
00:45:48,690 --> 00:45:51,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kana Arima would be 
a big hit on variety shows.</font>

717
00:45:51,820 --> 00:45:54,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Spread the work 
across everyone in the agency.</font>

718
00:45:55,160 --> 00:45:58,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Also, you should move to a bigger office.</font>

719
00:45:59,810 --> 00:46:02,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You gotta make 'em believe 
we're a major joint.</font>

720
00:46:04,110 --> 00:46:05,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm just not good enough.</font>

721
00:46:07,560 --> 00:46:11,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you'd run the agency all along, 
it would be so much bigger now.</font>

722
00:46:11,810 --> 00:46:14,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nah, you've done amazing.</font>

723
00:46:14,470 --> 00:46:17,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You built respectful 
working relationships with clients,</font>

724
00:46:17,810 --> 00:46:20,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">brought in work 
without stepping on any toes,</font>

725
00:46:20,470 --> 00:46:22,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and developed better 
talent in the meantime.</font>

726
00:46:23,630 --> 00:46:28,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Frankly, Strawberry Pro has a stellar 
reputation within the industry right now.</font>

727
00:46:28,520 --> 00:46:30,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Never would've happened with me in charge.</font>

728
00:46:31,160 --> 00:46:33,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It was only possible because of you.</font>

729
00:46:43,100 --> 00:46:46,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're not going to win me over 
with obvious sucking up like that.</font>

730
00:46:46,980 --> 00:46:50,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Once you're done here, you're cleaning 
the sinks and bathrooms.</font>

731
00:46:50,920 --> 00:46:53,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That wasn't what I was going for, really.</font>

732
00:46:55,180 --> 00:46:58,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Also, keep a close eye on that kid.</font>

733
00:46:58,980 --> 00:47:00,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know.</font>

734
00:47:00,700 --> 00:47:02,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's a difficult time for Ruby, but I—</font>

735
00:47:02,510 --> 00:47:03,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not her.</font>

736
00:47:03,630 --> 00:47:06,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's Aqua we need to keep an eye on.</font>

737
00:47:07,930 --> 00:47:11,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's gonna break down soon.</font>

738
00:47:11,390 --> 00:47:14,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hell, he might already have.</font>

739
00:47:17,690 --> 00:47:19,270
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="16"><font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#4a313f">The 15-Year Lie</font></font></font></b></font>

740
00:47:20,340 --> 00:47:23,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I don't know why, 
but this feels lacking somehow.</i></font>

741
00:47:24,680 --> 00:47:29,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Aqua-kun, will this really help you 
complete your revenge?</i></font>

742
00:47:30,950 --> 00:47:35,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Filming for <i>The 15-Year Lie</i> 
starts next week.</font>

743
00:47:35,690 --> 00:47:38,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's a massive project 
for Strawberry Pro as a whole.</font>

744
00:47:38,600 --> 00:47:41,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The day after tomorrow, we have the 
full read-through and costume checks.</font>

745
00:47:41,450 --> 00:47:43,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">At dawn in four days, 
we visit the shrine to pray for a hit.</font>

746
00:47:43,890 --> 00:47:45,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And filming starts in seven days.</font>

747
00:47:46,120 --> 00:47:49,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're scheduled to wrap 
in the third week of August.</font>

748
00:47:49,210 --> 00:47:50,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The last week is reserved as insurance.</font>

749
00:47:51,290 --> 00:47:53,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I smell a holiday incoming!</font>

750
00:47:54,800 --> 00:47:56,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But don't you forget.</font>

751
00:47:57,260 --> 00:48:00,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We have Kana-chan's graduation 
concert at the end of August.</font>

752
00:48:00,250 --> 00:48:03,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll be using the reserved days 
to practice for that.</font>

753
00:48:03,310 --> 00:48:05,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Uh, about that...</font>

754
00:48:05,990 --> 00:48:09,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We set up a B-Komachi live tour 
at the end of the year.</font>

755
00:48:09,010 --> 00:48:11,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's where Kana Arima 
will be graduating.</font>

756
00:48:12,330 --> 00:48:13,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The heck?</font>

757
00:48:13,530 --> 00:48:16,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We were all ready to say goodbye!</font>

758
00:48:16,580 --> 00:48:19,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We got Arima's okay.</font>

759
00:48:19,960 --> 00:48:24,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I mean, it's not like 
I <i>have</i> to leave in August.</font>

760
00:48:24,390 --> 00:48:26,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And we'll all be busy,</font>

761
00:48:26,580 --> 00:48:31,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so I'd feel bad asking you to make time 
for my graduation concert.</font>

762
00:48:31,830 --> 00:48:35,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How was I supposed to refuse 
when they insisted?</font>

763
00:48:35,780 --> 00:48:38,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here stands the most 
accommodating entertainer of all time.</font>

764
00:48:38,720 --> 00:48:40,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Pushover doesn't begin to describe her!</font>

765
00:48:40,760 --> 00:48:43,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Treat yourself better, girl!</font>

766
00:48:43,750 --> 00:48:47,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, plans never go according to plan.</font>

767
00:48:47,500 --> 00:48:48,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, Director.</font>

768
00:48:48,820 --> 00:48:50,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What brings you here today?</font>

769
00:48:50,790 --> 00:48:52,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nothing special.</font>

770
00:48:53,280 --> 00:48:55,750
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="14"><font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#2f1c36">The 15-Year Lie</font></font></font></b></font>

771
00:48:53,280 --> 00:48:55,750
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="13"><font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#2f1c36">Final Version</font></font></font></b></font>

772
00:48:53,590 --> 00:48:55,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I just brought the final script.</font>

773
00:48:55,750 --> 00:48:56,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whoa!</font>

774
00:48:56,960 --> 00:48:58,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You brought these personally?</font>

775
00:48:58,560 --> 00:49:00,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, our workplaces are nearby.</font>

776
00:49:01,790 --> 00:49:03,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And paying for a courier would be a waste.</font>

777
00:49:03,960 --> 00:49:08,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't wanna hear about the financial 
realities of a single man in his 40s.</font>

778
00:49:08,860 --> 00:49:11,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My name's really on here!</font>

779
00:49:11,660 --> 00:49:13,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can I really do this?</font>

780
00:49:13,890 --> 00:49:16,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't worry. You'll do just fine.</font>

781
00:49:16,040 --> 00:49:17,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kana-chan!</font>

782
00:49:17,270 --> 00:49:21,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've been playing the role of a high 
schooler all these years, after all.</font>

783
00:49:21,460 --> 00:49:23,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Those are two very different things!</font>

784
00:49:24,230 --> 00:49:29,570
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font color="#f6f4f1">m 0 0 l 100 0 100 100 0 100</font></b></font>

785
00:49:24,230 --> 00:49:29,570
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font face="Times New Roman"><font size="14"><font color="#695653">Ai (B-Komachi)
Takamiy (B-Komachi)
Nino (B-Komachi)
Mei-Mei (B-Komachi)
Boy A
Seijuurou Uehara
Airi Himekawa
Taiki Himekawa
Young Aqua
Young Ruby
Ichigo Saitou
Miyako Saitou
Doctor
Nurse</font></font></font></b></font>

786
00:49:24,230 --> 00:49:29,570
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font face="Times New Roman"><font size="14"><font color="#695653">Ruby Hoshino
Akane Kurokawa
Kana Arima
MEMcho
