Mei Adashino</font></font></font></b></font>

787
00:49:24,860 --> 00:49:28,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? There are still some 
empty spaces in the cast list.</font>

788
00:49:28,010 --> 00:49:29,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, you're right.</font>

789
00:49:29,860 --> 00:49:32,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, those are the kid roles.</font>

790
00:49:32,100 --> 00:49:34,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We just haven't been able 
to pencil those in.</font>

791
00:49:36,580 --> 00:49:40,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's so hard to find good child actors.</font>

792
00:49:40,620 --> 00:49:45,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've been screening them 
all over the country, but no dice.</font>

793
00:49:45,680 --> 00:49:49,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They stick out like a sore thumb when 
you give them lines in a serious movie.</font>

794
00:49:49,970 --> 00:49:53,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Child actors who can handle long lines 
with ease are worth their weight in gold.</font>

795
00:49:53,410 --> 00:49:54,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know what you mean.</font>

796
00:49:54,970 --> 00:50:01,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Quality films need child actors as good 
as me born in the same time frame!</font>

797
00:50:01,260 --> 00:50:05,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Must suck so hard for this era 
to have nobody on my level!</font>

798
00:50:05,440 --> 00:50:08,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Look at her cling to her past glories.</font>

799
00:50:08,740 --> 00:50:11,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I gotta go looking right after this, too.</font>

800
00:50:11,280 --> 00:50:12,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good luck!</font>

801
00:50:17,910 --> 00:50:20,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You look like you've steeled yourself.</font>

802
00:50:21,260 --> 00:50:25,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">To hurt people, and to be hurt in turn.</font>

803
00:50:26,600 --> 00:50:28,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you have nothing better to do?</font>

804
00:50:28,400 --> 00:50:30,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You keep showing up to grind my gears.</font>

805
00:50:31,190 --> 00:50:34,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm merely trying to guide you onto 
the right path toward your fate.</font>

806
00:50:35,450 --> 00:50:38,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fate, eh? What are you, 
a god or something?</font>

807
00:50:39,100 --> 00:50:44,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now, that depends on how 
you people define a "god."</font>

808
00:50:44,690 --> 00:50:46,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Different question.</font>

809
00:50:46,210 --> 00:50:48,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you have parents? A government ID?</font>

810
00:50:49,340 --> 00:50:50,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course.</font>

811
00:50:50,930 --> 00:50:55,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This vessel was born of a mother, 
much like you two.</font>

812
00:50:55,910 --> 00:50:57,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you want to check?</font>

813
00:50:57,450 --> 00:50:59,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's just another child's body 
you'd find anywhere.</font>

814
00:51:00,630 --> 00:51:01,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh.</font>

815
00:51:03,510 --> 00:51:04,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

816
00:51:05,600 --> 00:51:06,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Listen...</font>

817
00:51:07,360 --> 00:51:08,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wanna be a child actor?</font>

818
00:51:10,880 --> 00:51:11,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wha?</font>

819
00:51:12,920 --> 00:51:16,220
<font face="Times New Roman" size="32" color="#0a0a0a"><b>{\an8}<font color="#fafafa">Episode 35










The Beginning</font></b></font>

